Name: PGK_short
Description: Probability of being in Green Zone of Kobe Space (SB>SBMSY & F<FMSY) in years 1-10 (2025-2034)

Name: PGK_med
Description: Probability of being in Green Zone of Kobe Space (SB>SBMSY & F<FMSY) in years 11-20 (2035-2044)

Name: PGK_long
Description: Probability of being in Green Zone of Kobe Space (SB>SBMSY & F<FMSY) in years 21-30 (2045-2054)

Name: PGK
Description: Probability of being in Green Zone of Kobe Space (SB>SBMSY & F<FMSY) over all years (2025-2054)

Name: PGK_30
Description: Probability of being in Green Zone of Kobe Space (SB>SBMSY & F<FMSY) in year 30 (2054)

Name: POF
Description: Probability of Overfishing (F>FMSY) over all years (2025-2054)

Name: PNOF
Description: Probability of Not Overfishing (F<FMSY) over all years (2025-2054)

Name: LRP_short
Description: Probability of breaching the limit reference point (SB<0.4SBMSY) in any of the first 10 years (2025-2034)

Name: LRP_med
Description: Probability of breaching the limit reference point (SB<0.4SBMSY) in any of years 11-20 (2035-2044)

Name: LRP_long
Description: Probability of breaching the limit reference point (SB<0.4SBMSY) in any of years 21-30 (2045-2054)

Name: LRP
Description: Probability of breaching the limit reference point (SB<0.4SBMSY) in any year (2025-2054)

Name: TAC1
Description: TAC (t) in the first implementation year (2025)

Name: VarC
Description: Mean variation in TAC (%) between management cycles over all years and simulations
